---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Swag"
  meta_title="Sovereign Engineering Swag"
  description="Get your Sovereign Engineering merchandise - shirts, hoodies, and more"
  showCallToAction={false}
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Black Hat Image -->
  <header class="relative h-[420px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-black flex items-center justify-center">
    <img
      src="/images/swag/black-hat.webp"
      alt="Sovereign Engineering Black Hat Design"
      class="w-3/4 h-auto object-contain opacity-80"
    />
  </header>

  <!-- Products Section -->
  <section class="w-full text-white bg-black py-8 sm:py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 pt-8 text-center text-white font-normal">The Story of Our Swag</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4">
          This collection tells a story—the story of Sovereign Engineering. It's an chronicle of the
          <a href="/projects" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">tools we build</a>
          and the <a href="/philosophy" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">principles</a>
          we uphold. Each design is a chapter in our ongoing journey to create technology that empowers
          the individual and secures our digital freedom.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-01 Shirt - Left -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec01-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt.webp"
                alt="SEC-01 Shirt"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
              <button type="button" class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group border-none p-0" onclick="changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt')" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt')">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt.webp"
                  alt="SEC-01 Shirt"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                />
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group border-none p-0"
                onclick="changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt2.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt 2')"
                onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt2.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt 2')">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt2.webp"
                  alt="SEC-01 Shirt 2"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                />
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group border-none p-0"
                onclick="changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt3.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt 3')"
                onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec01-main', '/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt3.webp', 'SEC-01 Shirt 3')">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC01_Shirt3.webp"
                  alt="SEC-01 Shirt 3"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                />
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-01: The Beginning</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                It all starts with an idea and the will to build. This shirt is a tribute to that first step,
                the moment you decide to create something new instead of complaining about the old. It's a
                reminder that every journey begins with a single line of code, and that to build a better
                future, you must first be willing to
                <a href="/podcast" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">start ugly</a>.
              </p>
              <p>
                Perfection is the enemy of progress, and this design is a badge of honor for those who
                understand that. It's for the builders, the creators, and the pioneers who aren't afraid
                to ship imperfect things. It separates the talkers from the doers, and it's a public
                declaration that you are here to build.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-02 Hat - Right -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec02-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC02_Hat.webp"
                alt="SEC-02 Hat"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC02_Hat.webp"
                    alt="SEC-02 Hat"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat2.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat Variant 2')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat2.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat Variant 2')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC02_Hat2.webp"
                    alt="SEC-02 Hat Variant 2"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat3.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat Variant 3')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec02-main', '/images/swag/SEC02_Hat3.webp', 'SEC-02 Hat Variant 3')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC02_Hat3.webp"
                    alt="SEC-02 Hat Variant 3"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-02: Opsec Friendly</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                In a world of total surveillance, privacy is not a feature; it's a precondition for freedom.
                This hat is for those who understand that true sovereignty begins with operational security.
                It's a nod to the cypherpunks who taught us that
                <a href="https://dergigi.com/2020/07/21/true-names-not-required/" target="_blank"
                   rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">True Names</a>
                are not required.
              </p>
              <p>
                It's a subtle signal to those in the know, a quiet acknowledgment of the invisible war being
                waged for our minds and our data. It's a reminder to stay vigilant, to question authority,
                and to build systems that can't be evil. Stay low, stay safe, stay sovereign.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-03 Shirt - Left -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec03-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC03_Back.webp"
                alt="SEC-03 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Front.webp', 'SEC-03 Shirt Front')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Front.webp', 'SEC-03 Shirt Front')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC03_Front.webp"
                    alt="SEC-03 Shirt Front"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Back.webp', 'SEC-03 Shirt Back')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Back.webp', 'SEC-03 Shirt Back')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC03_Back.webp"
                    alt="SEC-03 Shirt Back"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-03: Ecash</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                Before Bitcoin, there was ecash. This design is a tribute to the pioneers who dreamed of
                digital cash and the cypherpunks who fought for it. The burning cassette symbolizes the
                creative destruction of the old financial system, a necessary step to build a new one on
                a foundation of freedom.
              </p>
              <p>
                For decades, ecash was a dream deferred, a powerful idea waiting for its moment. Bitcoin
                finally provided the missing piece: a trustless, decentralized bearer asset. Now, combined
                with a simple, open protocol like nostr, ecash is not just viable; it's a match made in
                heaven, ready to power a new generation of sovereign applications.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-04 Shirt - Right -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec04-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC04_Back.webp"
                alt="SEC-04 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Front.webp', 'SEC-04 Shirt Front')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Front.webp', 'SEC-04 Shirt Front')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC04_Front.webp"
                    alt="SEC-04 Shirt Front"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Back.webp', 'SEC-04 Shirt Back')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Back.webp', 'SEC-04 Shirt Back')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC04_Back.webp"
                    alt="SEC-04 Shirt Back"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-04: Trilemmas</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                There are <a href="/podcast" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">no perfect solutions</a>,
                only trade-offs. This shirt is a nod to the fundamental trilemmas that govern our world,
                from the classic
                <a href="https://press.rebus.community/requirementsengineering/chapter/the-engineering-triangle/"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">Good, Fast, Cheap</a>
                to the
                <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impossible_trinity" target="_blank"
                   rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">impossible trinity</a>
                of monetary policy. It's an acknowledgment that reality has constraints, and that pretending
                otherwise is a recipe for disaster.
              </p>
              <p>
                The compass reminds us that while the path may be fraught with impossible choices, we must
                always navigate by the star of our principles. It's about making conscious, informed
                trade-offs, not wishful thinking. Understanding these constraints is the first step to
                overcoming them.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-05 Shirt - Left -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec05-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC05_Back.webp"
                alt="SEC-05 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Front.webp', 'SEC-05 Shirt Front')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Front.webp', 'SEC-05 Shirt Front')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC05_Front.webp"
                    alt="SEC-05 Shirt Front"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <button type="button" class="border-none p-0 bg-transparent cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Back.webp', 'SEC-05 Shirt Back')"
                  onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' ') changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Back.webp', 'SEC-05 Shirt Back')">
                  <img
                    src="/images/swag/SEC05_Back.webp"
                    alt="SEC-05 Shirt Back"
                    class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-05: YOLO Mode</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                The future is not something you wait for; it's something you build. This design is for
                those who are done asking for permission and are ready to enter
                <a href="https://www.thewayofcode.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">YOLO mode</a>, building the world
                they want to live in, starting now.
              </p>
              <p>
                Because Bitcoin and nostr are permissionless, we don't have to ask for anyone's approval
                to build. This allows us to lean heavily into the vibe, creating systems that are not
                only uncensorable but also aligned with our vision of a freer, more sovereign future.
                This shirt is a declaration that we're not here to reform the old system; we're here to
                make it obsolete.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="pt-2 pb-32 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="container max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                   <a
               href="https://plebeian.market/community/_@sovereignengineering.io/sovereign-engineering-swag-s4tjghja1r"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="btn-retro px-8 py-4"
             >
        Visit Webshop →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<script is:inline>
  // Function to change main image
  // @ts-expect-error - Astro script context doesn't support TypeScript types
  function changeMainImage(elementId, imageSrc, imageAlt) {
    const mainImage = document.getElementById(elementId);
    if (mainImage && mainImage.tagName === 'IMG') {
      // @ts-expect-error - HTMLElement type doesn't include img properties
      mainImage.src = imageSrc;
      // @ts-expect-error - HTMLElement type doesn't include img properties
      mainImage.alt = imageAlt;
    }
  }

  // Expose the function to the global scope so inline onclick handlers can access it
  // @ts-expect-error - window is global
  window.changeMainImage = changeMainImage;
</script>
